{
  "bookId": "heshanggong-laozi",
  "num": 23,
  "title": "第二十三章（虛無）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "希言自然。"
    },
    {
      "text": "故飄風不終朝，驟雨不終日。"
    },
    {
      "text": "孰為此者？天地。"
    },
    {
      "text": "天地尚不能久，"
    },
    {
      "text": "而況於人乎？"
    },
    {
      "text": "故從事於道者，"
    },
    {
      "text": "道者同於道，"
    },
    {
      "text": "德者同於德，"
    },
    {
      "text": "失者同於失。"
    },
    {
      "text": "同於道者，道亦樂得之。"
    },
    {
      "text": "同於德者，德亦樂得之，"
    },
    {
      "text": "同於失者，失亦樂得之。"
    },
    {
      "text": "信不足焉，"
    },
    {
      "text": "有不信焉。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "希言者，謂愛言也。愛言者，自然之道。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 13
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "飄風，疾風也。驟雨，暴雨也。 言疾不能長，暴不能久也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "孰，誰也。誰為此飄風暴雨者乎？天地所為。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不能終於朝暮也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天地至神合為飄風暴雨，尚不能使終朝至暮，何況人欲為暴卒乎。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "從，為也。人為事當如道安靜，不當如飄風驟雨也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "道者，謂好道人也。同於道者，所謂與道同也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "德者，謂好德之人也。同於德者，所謂與德同也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "失，謂任己而失人也。同於失者，所謂與失同也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "與道同者，道亦樂得之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 10,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "與德同者，德亦樂得之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-12",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "與失同者，失亦樂失之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-13",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 12,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "君信不足於下，下則應君以不信也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-14",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 13,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "此言物類相歸，同聲相應，同氣相求。雲從龍，風從虎，水流濕，火就燥，自然之類也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
